'''亨利·圖阿克烏·普納'''（{{lang-en|Henry Tuakeu Puna}}<ref>[http://www.stats.gov.ck/NewsEvents/Rolls/22Manihiki.pdf Parliamentary General Election – Main Electoral Roll – Manihiki] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stats.gov.ck/NewsEvents/Rolls/22Manihiki.pdf |date=20101001070142 }}, Cook Islands Registrar of Electors, 10 May 2010.</ref>；{{bd|1949年|8月6日|}}<ref name=cinsworn/>），是一名[[庫克群島|庫克群島]]政治人物。

他在{{le|2004年庫克群島大選|Cook Islands general election, 2004}}{{le|曼尼希基 (庫克群島議會選區)|Manihiki (Cook Islands electorate)|曼尼希基選區}}首次參選，競逐前總理{{le|罗伯特·温顿|Robert Woonton}}的議席<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=11968 |title=Cooks opposition warns of prime minister losing seat over pearl industry decline |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2004-09-06 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpAOMRm?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最初他以微弱劣勢敗選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=12106 |title=Cooks PM Woonton retains seat |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2004-09-14 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpB2keK?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他提出選舉呈請挑戰結果<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=12307 |title=Cook Islands prime minister named in election petition |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2004-09-23 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpBdLIl?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來呈請決定維持原判，但因為有部分選民喪失投票資格，令重新點票結果出現平局<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=13735 |title=Cooks to vote for new Prime Minister after election draw leads to by-election |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2004-12-12 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524011855/http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=13735 |archive-date=2012-05-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，需要進行{{le|2005年曼尼希基補選|Manihiki by-election 2005|補選}}；補選中普納終於勝出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=14781 |title=Preliminary results show Puna wins Cook Islands by-election |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2005-02-10 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpD1I0s?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>，唯{{le|2006年庫克群島大選|Cook Islands general election, 2006|2006年大選}}裡他的議席敗給{{le|阿皮伊·皮奧|Apii Piho}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=27171 |title=Leader of Cook Islands Party at a loss over election result |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2006-10-01 |accessdate=2010-01-05 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpEEpAs?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他在{{le|2010年庫克群島大選|Cook Islands general election, 2010|2010年大選}}再次當選為曼尼希基選區議員，並在11月30日宣誓就任[[庫克群島總理列表|庫克群島總理]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=57367 |title=New Cook Islands PM sworn in |publisher=Radio New Zealand International |date=2010-11-30 |accessdate=2010-12-01 |archive-date=2012-09-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AOpEq0E8?url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後再在2014和2018年大選後續任，直至2020年因尋求當選[[太平洋島國論壇|太平洋島國論壇]]秘書長而辭職，並於翌年當選秘書長。

